Bump json5, css-loader and html-webpack-plugin (#188)

Bumps [json5](https://github.com/json5/json5) to 2.2.3 and updates ancestor dependencies [json5](https://github.com/json5/json5), [css-loader](https://github.com/webpack-contrib/css-loader) and [html-webpack-plugin](https://github.com/jantimon/html-webpack-plugin). These dependencies need to be updated together.
